{"tid":2439093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"69歲染疫翁昏迷中「連續硬3小時」突病逝！　醫：新冠釀異常勃起","createTime":"2021-03-09T03:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:19:53.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"989ad0b11f14adc174c9cbda11de046944e5f7a3","tid":2439093,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"美國一名染疫的6旬老翁日前在住院治療時，於昏迷的狀態下出現陰莖異常勃起症狀，儘<br />\n管醫護人員拿出冰敷袋放在病患的生殖器上，試圖減緩腫脹，但老翁仍持續勃起了3個小<br />\n時，醫師最後只好拿出針頭，試圖從生殖器中抽出部分血液，然而異常勃起症狀尚未減緩<br />\n，老翁便因肺衰竭死亡。<br />\n <br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，美國一名醫師日前在《美國醫學雜誌》（American Journal of<br />\nAmerican Medicine）中提到，他與團隊認為，新冠病毒會導致男性病患的生殖器出現血<br />\n塊，造成陰莖異常勃起的症狀。這名醫師稱，他的病患在昏迷狀態下勃起長達3小時，儘<br />\n管他們嘗試了一些治療方法，但最後還沒能減緩陰莖異常勃起症狀，患者就肺衰竭病逝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210309/1934013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210309%2F1934013.htm&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=1d629185\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210309/1934013.htm</a>"},{"pid":"57f795779e242ba0213275450f9a6e40f88a0ed6","tid":2439093,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"想死前嚟多q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb9c10e160ee6bbf4f4e98801181210476322a5","tid":2439093,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"只好拿出針頭，試圖從生殖器中抽出部分血液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039cc3b133a3942a6d0b8d3eab7bc61c27af6dce","tid":2439093,"uid":6260,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"疫苗壯陽 遲早比大陸人拎哂黎炒餸"},{"pid":"41a2af234f0416e03a5afa0d1bb688fbde8bd9f8","tid":2439093,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal